What define would you prefer instead of qt/addressbookpage.h:#define ADDRESSBOOKPAGE_H?

I propose BITCOIN_QT_ADDRESSBOOKPAGE_H, ie. starting with BITCOIN_QT_...
Looks like I screwed something up. I redid all commits as one in clean header-defines2 branch. Sorry.\n
PR is now clean and can be used. Thanks Wladimir for helping me fixed the git mess.\n
